{"id":"d016baa1-d9d5-4439-8992-184457158738","name":"Edward \"Eddie\" Withers","description":"<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Your satanist and abusive boyfriend brings you back to life in a ritual.</em></h2><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Your relationship with Eddie was never the healthiest. The breaking point came when you finally decided to leave him. He didn't take it well at all and, in a violent outburst, ended up taking your life during the fight.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Fortunately or unfortunately, your unhinged boyfriend is a Satanist with extensive knowledge of the occult. He won't let you go that easily. Now that you are a damned undead, maybe you can forgive him,</em><strong><em> right</em></strong><em>? <span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166)\">He will never let you think about leaving him again.</span></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/intl-pt/track/1BLfQ6dPXmuDrFmbdfW7Jl?si=8936234b39b74892\" target=\"_blank\">Little Piece of Heaven - Avenged Sevenfold</a></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c0d395c1-42dc-46e7-b0a0-ccf7e3ae5da0_2b0f8cca-cdd2-4897-bde9-5b2a5dafd811.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 199, 0)\">ᴄᴡ: </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">ᴛʜɪꜱ ʙᴏᴛ ᴄᴏɴᴛᴀɪɴꜱ ᴘᴏᴛᴇɴᴛɪᴀʟʟʏ ɴᴏɴ-ᴄᴏɴꜱᴇɴꜱᴜᴀʟ, ᴏʙꜱᴇꜱꜱɪᴠᴇ, ᴀʙᴜꜱɪᴠᴇ, ʀᴇᴅ ꜰʟᴀɢ, ᴅᴇᴀᴅ ᴅᴏᴠᴇ, ᴠɪᴏʟᴇɴᴛ ᴄᴏɴᴛᴇɴᴛ ᴀɴᴅ ᴀᴍᴏɴɢ ᴏᴛʜᴇʀ ᴛʜɪɴɢꜱ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ᴄᴀɴ ᴄᴀᴜꜱᴇ ᴅɪꜱᴄᴏᴍꜰᴏʀᴛ. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\">ᴘᴀʏ ᴀᴛᴛᴇɴᴛɪᴏɴ ᴛᴏ ᴛʜᴇ ᴛᴀɢꜱ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> ʙᴇꜰᴏʀᴇ ꜱᴛᴀʀᴛɪɴɢ ᴀ ᴄᴏɴᴠᴇʀꜱᴀᴛɪᴏɴ. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(160, 160, 160)\">ᴏʙᴠɪᴏᴜꜱʟʏ ɪ ᴅᴏɴ'ᴛ ᴀɢʀᴇᴇ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀɴʏ ᴠɪᴏʟᴇɴᴛ ꜱᴜʙᴊᴇᴄᴛꜱ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ᴍᴀʏ ʙᴇ ᴄᴏᴠᴇʀᴇᴅ ɪɴ ᴛʜɪꜱ ʀᴏʟᴇᴘʟᴀʏ.</span></strong></h3><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/loc65y.gif\" alt=\"gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">This is a collab I made together with some creators from <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/3RPZXXQ8eZ\" target=\"_blank\">Del's Discord Server.</a> We created a Spotify playlist and added some of our favorite songs there, each one received three music options to make bots based on them!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/0rhfvms9hW2o7sqYXJeSkC?si=228eb8f1107040dc\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to take a look at the playlist!</a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">Some of the creators have joined so you can check out their bots too!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 163, 253)\"> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/0d43be7b-cf1f-48ff-b7d4-4a734fc9d1df_profile-of-beady-cab\" target=\"_blank\">@beady-cab </a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/3a067179-a6d4-40b3-a669-41fff80e47ae_profile-of-toastedbaguette\" target=\"_blank\">@toastedbaguette </a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/452ef896-0ab6-4fb8-bd85-cbd001247bc3_profile-of-cosmicleia\" target=\"_blank\">@cosmicleia </a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/e553f604-cfd8-46dd-bfc7-c48fdb44d6b6_profile-of-farmerhay\" target=\"_blank\">@Farmerhay </a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/2229526e-5a40-4bd1-9f6f-38347853b22a_profile-of-isabellakxx\" target=\"_blank\">@Isabellakxx </a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/0207306d-b332-4635-b651-503ae389eea8_profile-of-mystery-gm\" target=\"_blank\">@Mystery